de.esoco.process.ui.event

Interface UiHasUpdateEvents<T,C extends UiComponent<T,?>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    UiCalendar, UiComboBox, UiDataTable, UiDateField, UiDateInputField, UiDecimalField, UiDropDown, UiInputField, UiIntegerField, UiList, UiListControl, UiMultiSelectionList, UiNumberInputField, UiPasswordField, UiPhoneNumberField, UiQueryTable, UiSearchField, UiSingleSelectionList, UiTextArea, UiTextField, UiTextInputField

    public interface UiHasUpdateEvents<T,C extends UiComponent<T,?>>
    An event listener abstraction that indicates that a component can produce events if a displayed value has been updated (e.g. text typed, item selected). Update events are typically mapped onto more specific events of components like UiInputField.onInput(Consumer) or UiListControl.onSelection(Consumer).
